Interface PersistentSet<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<T>, Iterable<T>, Set<T>, Traversable<T>

    public interface PersistentSet<T>
extends Set<T>, Traversable<T>
    A read only set structure where mutation is expression. Side effecting mutation throws UnsupportedOperationException
